::Battera::

She looked up and the shark and it startled her.
"AHH"
She let go of the branch and fell a few feet, opened up her wings and glided 
to the ground.
"Sorry about that.  You startled me. I'm fine."

She looked at the ground for a moment and then to her wing.
"well, on second thought, I could do with a bit of repair work.  I seamed to 
have damaged my left wing."

::CyberShark::

    Floating outside the fight he saw a very large bat fly and land in a
tree. He decided to go in to investigate. Lowering himself to greet this 
bat.
He scanned the trees to see exactly where it landed. The only reason he was
so interested was that it was defintly a strange mix of colors for a bat.
Which meant Robot in Disguise. The scanners picked up it's signal and it
turned out to be Predacon.
    "Hey, are you all right? What's the matter?"
